@AuthMicroservice_HostAddress = http://localhost:5090

### Registrar novo usuário
POST {{AuthMicroservice_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "guilherme",
  "email": "guilherme@email.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### Login
POST {{AuthMicroservice_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "guilherme@email.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### Obter usuário autenticado (substituir <TOKEN> pelo JWT retornado)
GET {{AuthMicroservice_HostAddress}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>

### Refresh token
POST {{AuthMicroservice_HostAddress}}/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accessToken": "<ACCESS_TOKEN>",
  "refreshToken": "<REFRESH_TOKEN>"
}

### Revogar token (requer autenticação)
POST {{AuthMicroservice_HostAddress}}/api/auth/revoke
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>

###
